Title: Hungry in Hollow
Description:
Hey. You looking for a great meal?

Willing to wade through the mud to get it?

Go see Dolena. She'll sort you out. Don't bother trying to convince her to leave that hollow, though. Believe me--we've all tried. Why someone would leave the safety of the light for that...

She seems to do alright, though.
ObjectivesText: Seek out Dolena in Growling Hollow
RewardText: Ah, another one. You here on purpose?
